On ‎7‎/‎16‎/‎2018 at 6:57 AM, Cyclic3 said:

Hi all,

I was going through my old disks the other day, and I came across an old complete dump of * (the old mod site), downloaded when the torrent for the site was still up. I was planning on deleting it, unless anyone had any use for it. Please let me know ASAP if you want a copy of all or part of it. Be warned that the full thing is >60GB uncompressed, and so I won't be able to just email it.

It would be a shame for this monument of KSP's history to be destroyed, particularly since I cannot find it anywhere else. However, I really need the space, and so if I don't get a response soon, I will nuke it.
